\v  ]) 	[[:upper:]]    upper case (== [A-Z]) 	[[:word:]]     word characters (== [0-9A-Za-z_]) 	[[:xdigit:]]   hex digit (== [0-9A-Fa-f])  Unicode character classes are those in [unicode.Categories], [unicode.CategoryAliases], and [unicode.Scripts].
